column2: the  prosecution  has  failed  to  prove  beyond  reasonable  doubt  the  person  named
Mohammed Nazeer Carder is in fact Mohammad Moujeed Amir Irshad,  6th accused-
the learned Trial Judge has got himself mislead on the facts and he could not come in
to the conclusion that the prosecution has proved beyond reasonable doubt that the
person named Mohammed Nazeer Carder is in fact Mohammad Moujeed Amir Irshad,
